title: 8th place team on Kibo RPC 2021 (Lynx)
body: Write a java program to make Astrobee robot do designated tasks on ISS simulation.

title: 3rd place team on Kibo RPC 2022 (Lynx)
body:
Write a java program to make Astrobee robot do designated tasks on ISS simulation which there's a need to do 
image processing, robot movement error handling, and robot route planning.
